What is a Database? How to create and use a Database?
   -- A Database is an organized collection of Data. It can be accessed or Stored in a computer system. It can be 
   managed through a Database Management system (DBMS), a software which is used to Manage Data.

   -- Create a Database
   Query: Create Database Databasename;

   -- Display Existing Database
   Query: SHOW databases;

   -- Use a Database
   Query: use Databasename

   --Show Selected Database
   Query: Select Database()

   -- Delete a Database
   Query: Drop Database Databasename;



